# Build context exclusions (LNG-216-LOGIN).
# Primary purpose: keep Docker from walking heavy / non-shippable dirs. The
# backend .venv in particular must be excluded — a stale NFS handle on it
# otherwise hangs the build-context load indefinitely.

# Python virtualenvs & caches
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.mypy_cache

# Node / frontend build artifacts (the image rebuilds these from source)
**/node_modules
frontend/.next
frontend/out

# VCS & tooling
.git
.github
**/.DS_Store

# Local data / logs / knowledge graph output
*.log
*.db
backend/data
graphify-out
